        {
          "type": "explanation",
          "name": "camera shaking",
          "definition": "The wobble function and weight affects how the camera shake oscilates over time.\nIf the weight is one, then the wobble function completely scales the translational\nand rotational magnitudes.  The less the weight, the less the effect wobble has.\nIf the wobble weight is 0 then wobble is completely ignored."
        },
